1) can we use ngIf/ngFor without asterisk(*)?
   <p *ngIf="condition">
      Our heroes are true!
   </p>
---->angular converts * into template tag, like given below:
   <ng-template  [ngIf]="condition">
   <p>
      Our heroes are true!
   </p>
   </ng-template>
          (or)
  <template [ngIf]="condition">
    <p>
      Our heroes are true!
    </p>
  </template>


